WHAT  — The uncrowned King of Malkier and Moiraine's Warder, the deadliest blademaster in the books.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the companions — the worldly people of the world, the fallen realm of Malkier  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
